sequenceDiagram
    participant Judge
    participant GameService
    participant GameState
    participant AI as AI Service
    participant WS as WebSocket
    participant FE as Frontend

    Note over Judge,FE: === Bug #1: 猎人最后神职不能开枪 ===
    
    Judge->>GameService: resolve_night / resolve_vote_round
    Note over GameService: 猎人死亡，设置 pending_hunter_shoot
    GameService->>GameState: pending_hunter_shoot = hunter_id

    Judge->>Judge: _handle_hunter_shoot()
    Judge->>Judge: _check_hunter_last_god()
    Note over Judge: 检查：除猎人外，存活神职是否为0
    
    alt 猎人是最后神职
        Judge->>GameState: pending_hunter_shoot = None
        Judge->>FE: 公告"猎人作为最后神职不能开枪"
    else 猎人不是最后神职
        Judge->>Judge: 正常开枪流程
    end

    Note over Judge,FE: === Bug #2: 预言家不能连续验同一人 ===
    
    FE->>WS: night_action {targetId}
    WS->>GameService: record_night_action()
    GameService->>GameService: 检查 consecutive_target_allowed
    GameService->>GameService: 比对 player.last_prophet_target_id
    
    alt 连续验同一人
        GameService-->>WS: 400 "预言家不能连续两晚查验同一目标"
    else 正常
        GameService->>GameState: 记录夜间行动
    end

    GameService->>GameService: resolve_night()
    GameService->>GameState: 更新 player.last_prophet_target_id

    Note over Judge,FE: === Bug #3: 白天发言顺序 ===
    
    Judge->>Judge: speak_phase()
    Judge->>Judge: 检查是否有警长

    alt 有警长(真人)
        Judge->>FE: broadcast speak_direction_request
        FE->>WS: speak_direction {direction: "left"/"right"}
        WS->>GameState: speak_direction = direction
    else 有警长(AI)
        Judge->>GameState: speak_direction = random("left"/"right")
    else 无警长
        Judge->>Judge: first_dead_player_id 决定起点
    end

    Judge->>GameService: _alive_speak_order(sheriff_id, direction, first_dead)
    GameService-->>Judge: speak_order 列表
    Judge->>Judge: 按顺序发言

    Note over Judge,FE: === Bug #5: 竞选发言退水 ===
    
    loop 每个候选人发言
        Judge->>FE: broadcast sheriff_speech_turn {canWithdraw: true}
        alt 候选人选择退水
            FE->>WS: sheriff_campaign {action: "withdraw"}
            WS->>GameService: withdraw_sheriff_campaign()
            GameService->>GameState: 从 candidate_ids 移除
            GameService-->>FE: broadcast 退水通知
        else 正常发言
            FE->>WS: speak {content: ...}
        end
    end

    Note over Judge,FE: === Bug #7: AI投票信息增强 ===
    
    Judge->>AI: _generate_ai_vote()
    AI->>GameState: 获取 game.chats(发言摘要) + game.votes(投票状态)
    AI->>AI: 构建 prompt 包含发言摘要+投票状态+白痴翻牌+警长信息
    AI-->>Judge: 投票目标

    Note over Judge,FE: === Bug #9: 猎人开枪胜负检查 ===
    
    FE->>WS: hunter_shoot {targetId}
    WS->>GameState: target.is_alive = False
    WS->>GameService: _check_win_condition()
    
    alt 游戏结束
        WS->>FE: broadcast game_over
    else 游戏继续
        WS->>GameState: 检查被枪杀者是否警长
    end
